data.description: Amazing "Nisqually Meadows" Home! You will love this 4 bedroom home from the inside out. You're immediately greeted by light & bright laminate hardwood floors throughout the main floor. Open concept kitchen with tons of storage & counter space. Family room offers lots of room to relax & play, w/ a warm & cozy gas fireplace. Upstairs you have all 4 bedrooms. Master suite includes a master bath and walk-in closet. Fully fenced backyard will wow you and all of your guests. Enjoy the garden space & fruit trees-or just sit back and enjoy the covered back porch. Home comes complete with all appliances, newer high efficiency furnace & AC systems. Close access to walking trails, freeways, shopping and military bases.
